AI Resume Screening System – Knowledge Base
1. Overview
An AI Resume Screening System helps recruiters evaluate candidates automatically using
AI-based pipelines.
2. Key Features
• Extract skills, tools, and experience • Match candidates with job descriptions • Assign fit score
(0–100) • Provide explainable results
3. Workflow
Resume ® Skill Extraction ® Matching ® Scoring ® Explanation
4. Technologies Used
LangChain, FastAPI, Python, LLMs
5. Benefits
• Faster hiring process • Reduced manual effort • Improved decision-making
6. Limitations
• Depends on input quality • May require tuning for accuracy
